1953;;The Veils of Bagdad;;American;;George Sherman;;Victor Mature, Mari Blanchard;;action drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Veils_of_Bagdad;;Antar is sent by Selima, head of the Ottoman Empire, to prevent Pasha Hammam from attempting to overthrow the emperor.<br><br>Selima blames Hammam and his assassin Kasseim for the death of her father.<br><br>Kasseim's wife, Rosanna, falls in love with Antar, but he wants Selima for himself.